{{Use Indian English|date=July 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date=July 2015}} {{notability|Biographies|date=April 2014}} {{Infobox person | name = Janvi Chheda | image = JanviChheda.jpg | caption = Chheda on the set of ''CID'' in November 2012 | birth_date = | birth_place = [[Mandvi]], [[Kutch]], [[Gujarat]], [[India]] | occupation = [[Actress]] | residence = [[Mumbai, Maharashtra]], India | known_for = ''[[Balika Vadhu]]'',''[[CID (Indian TV series)|CID]]'' | years_active = 2007–present | spouse = Nishant Gopalia | children = 1 }}
'''Janvi Chheda''' is an [[Indian people|Indian]] [[television]] [[actress]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/Actor-Janvi-Chheda-aka-Sugna-of-Balika-Vadhu-to-wed-on-22nd-of-November-with-her-boyfriend-Nishant-/articleshow/8988528.cms|title=Actor Janvi Chheda aka Sugna of Balika Vadhu to wed on 22nd of November with her boyfriend Nishant|author=Amrita Mulchandani|date=25 June 2011 |accessdate=20 November 2018 |work=[[The Times of India]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/gujarati/Actresses-who-shot-to-fame-from-Gujarati-TV/photostory/46046221.cms|title=Actresses who shot to fame from Gujarati TV - The Times of India|author=|date=28 January 2015 |accessdate=20 November 2018|work=[[The Times of India]]}}</ref>
She was in ''[[CID (Indian TV series)|CID]]'' as Inspector Shreya. Her first episode in ''CID'' was "Secret Of Head And Hand" which was aired on 30 June 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/daya-sir-my-favorite-says-janvi-chheda|title=Daya Sir is my favorite, says Janvi Chheda|author=Tellychakkar Team|date=27 June 2012|work=tellychakkar.com |accessdate=20 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WOoKTaL8ado |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713085744/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WOoKTaL8ado |dead-url=yes |archive-date=13 July 2012 |title=YouTube |author= |date= |work=youtube.com |df= }}</ref> Shreya in ''CID'' was shown as a brave and intelligent officer who could handle personal and professional life with the same ease. Janvi Chheda is now widely recognized for her role in ''CID'' as Inspector Shreya.
==Personal life== Janvi Chheda is a [[Gujarati people|Gujarati]] whose native place is [[Mandvi]], [[Kutch]].<ref name=toi>{{cite news|url=http://epaper.timesofindia.com/Default/Layout/Includes/TOI/ArtWin.asp?From=Archive&Source=Page&Skin=TOI&BaseHref=TOIA%2F2010%2F10%2F29&ViewMode=HTML&PageLabel=26&EntityId=Ar02600&AppName=1|title=‘I WOULDN’T MIND DOING SOUTH INDIAN FILMS’|first=Shruti|last=Jambhekar|publisher=[[The Times of India]]}}</ref> She was born and brought up in Mumbai but visited Mandvi as a child, where she celebrated [[Diwali]] for a number of years. She also loves to travel. She eats [[Gujarati cuisine|all kinds of cuisines]] at home.<ref name=toi />
She married her long-time beau Nishant Gopalia in 2011 with whom she has a daughter, Nirvi, born in 2017.<ref>{{cite web |title=Congratulations! CID actress Janvi Chheda becomes mother of a baby girl |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/television/celebrity/story/congratulation-cid-actress-janvi-chheda-becomes-a-mother-of-a-baby-girl-lifetv-1080914-2017-11-07 |website=[[India Today]] |author=Shweta Keshri |date=7 November 2017 |accessdate=20 November 2018}}</ref>
==Television== Janvi Chheda started her career as an anchor for a Gujarati television channel, and then did Gujarati TV shows, after which she made her way to the Hindi show Chhoona Hai Aasman.<ref name=toi />
